12:
No... I was originally made not to
require sleep anyway.
15:
Originally, huh... 
Well, the Stella I know eats 
and sleeps a ton.
17:
And I'm pretty sure she can still do
both of those things.
21:
I thought looking at the world like
this would help me remember.
23:
But what I did to that person... The
memories and convictions I threw
away... None of it can be undone.
44:
Stella, Alk, I've come to fulfill my
promise.
49:
I take it the rebuilding efforts are
proceeding apace?
58:
Why'd you hesitate? You telling me
everything's not tidied up yet?
61:
Ah, yes... It'd be ideal for everything
to have been sorted, wouldn't it...
63:
To be a simple process—finish one
job, move onto the next.
67:
But the truth is not so kind. Once you
finish one thing, two... three more
issues pop up! The more you work,
the more the mountain builds!
75:
Joking aside, I have appointed
qualified individuals to oversee the
important duties in my absence.
78:
The remaining work is mostly
formalities that require a royal
signature.
82:
In other words, you're
procrastinating. Never knew you
had it in you.
87:
If she has a system in place to
handle matters, I don't see why we
can't have her join us now.
101:
Yeah, great idea! We should eat out!
Get our party on!
105: May I make a selfish request?
110: Eh, you're the guest of honor. Shoot.
114:
I'd like to eat spicy game meat
roasted in leaves.
117:
Stella, Shakari taught you the recipe,
didn't she?
122:
Did... Did I say something wrong?
Why is everyone looking at me?
126:
Your request will put... everyone at
life-threatening risk...
136: Eh, you know what? Go for it, Stella.
139: You did it once, you can do it again.
142:
I believe in you! So just believe in the
me that believes in you!
151:
I-it's the surroundings! We gotta
have everything exactly the same,
that way she can recreate the
situation!
154:
Come on, let's head over to Light's
world!
165: Awesome! You landed it this time!
170:
Cut the meat. Coat it in honey. Wrap
it in leaves. Leave it by the fire—
177:
You didn't toast it into charcoal! Nice
job!
188:
Just like Shakari used to make it... 
It's  fantastic!
201:
I'm sorry... I know I'm not normal... I
must be broken—
219: All right. I'll prepare more right away!
224:
Whew! That was more like an
adventure than a welcome party,
huh?
228:
Indeed. There was merit in causing
trouble to come here.
232:
So you weren't actually kidding
about the work. Figured as much,
my fellow liar.
236:
...That world is going to reach its
limit at some point in the near future.
239:
Adjudicus and I are of the same
mind—we need a new place for our
people to live.
241:
Which means I, too, will need to fight
the Overlords.
244: So let us fight together. And Stella...
247:
I'm counting on you to watch my
back.
255:
Allow me to officially welcome you
to Starview Village, Lilith.
